                            <comment id="13874500" author="daijy" created="Fri, 17 Jan 2014 06:35:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Attach the final patch after review.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13874510" author="daijy" created="Fri, 17 Jan 2014 06:42:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch committed to trunk. Created &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3674&quot; title=&quot;Fix TestAccumuloPigCluster on Hadoop 2&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-3674&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-3674&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; to fix TestAccumuloPigCluster on Hadoop 2 and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3675&quot; title=&quot;Documentation for AccumuloStorage&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-3675&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-3675&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; for documentation. Thanks Josh!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13876034" author="cheolsoo" created="Sun, 19 Jan 2014 22:36:37 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=daijy&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;daijy&quot;&gt;Daniel Dai&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=elserj&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;elserj&quot;&gt;Josh Elser&lt;/a&gt;, this commit breaks unit tests in jenkins. Since TestAccumuloPigCluster does not shut down the mini cluster, sub-sequential tests fail with the following error-&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
java.net.ConnectException: Call to localhost/127.0.0.1:54029 failed on connection exception: java.net.ConnectException: Connection refused
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here 127.0.0.1:54029 is the NN that is used by TestAccumuloPigCluster and no longer exists, but sub-sequential tests (e.g. TestInputSizeReducerEstimator) try to talk to it.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Attaching a fix.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13876035" author="cheolsoo" created="Sun, 19 Jan 2014 22:37:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Please review &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-3573&quot; title=&quot;Provide StoreFunc and LoadFunc for Accumulo&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;PIG-3573&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;PIG-3573&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;-hotfix.patch&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
